Master Answer:
While some protection is gained after the 1st and 2nd doses, three doses of the HPV vaccine are needed for full protection in people 15 years of age and older. You can find more information on the HPV vaccine here. 
For more information on other ways to reduce your risk of HPV, visit the Smart Sex Resource website. 
Immunization Nurse
